summary: Can we have a Mamma Mia story, with Jon inviting three people who he believes are his dad's his mum hasn't told him, Robert...
question: Can we have a Mamma Mia story, with Jon inviting three people who he believes are his dad's his mum hasn't told him, Robert Bartheon, Arthur Dayne and Rheagar Targaryen to his wedding, he's getting married to Theon.   Elia and Lyanna helped raised Jon, Rhaenys and Aegon, but not tell Jon that Rheagar is his father.   In the end Jon and Theon do not get married in the end but Elia Martell and Lyanna Stark do.

blog.title: Dream of Ice and Fire
blog.description:
I am a Stark of Winterfell

I am a writer of Jonsa

body:
Conversations with Myself

I give up. I can’t possible ship this anymore. It’s too painful.

I know, but… look at these two 👀 look at each other 👀 👀

It won’t work out, it can’t, it’s too soft, too heavy too *inserts all the adjectives

Reread all the books! Re watch all the shows! Find all the clues! Save yourself….

Oh. My.

Stop.

Maybe I’ll just read some fan fiction. Can’t hurt, right?!

Maybe I’ll just write some fan fiction. I’ll work it out on the page!!!

Jonsa is actually endgame so just stop talking.
